Bean sprouts: 1 cup, blanched;
Mushrooms (shiitake or button): 1 cup, sliced;
Eggs: 2;
Garlic: 2 cloves, minced;
Soy sauce: 3 tbsp;
Sesame oil: 2 tbsp;
Vegetable oil: 2 tbsp;
