Fried shallots: for garnish;
Lime wedges: to serve;
Cucumber slices: to serve

instructions:
Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat; Add shallots, garlic, and red chili; sauté until fragrant and golden;
Add beef or mutton pieces and stir-fry until they start to brown;
Add curry powder, turmeric, coriander powder, cinnamon stick, cardamom, cloves, star anise, and lemongrass; stir well to coat the meat with spices;
Pour in water or beef broth; add kaffir lime leaves and tamarind juice; bring to a boil;
